snippet: Mark Noble's penalty earned West Ham United a smash-and-grab 1-0 victory over Hull City after the luckless visitors were denied three times by the woodwork at the London Stadium on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Mark Noble's penalty earned West Ham United a smash-and-grab 1-0 victory over Hull City after the luckless visitors were denied three times by the woodwork at the London Stadium on Saturday.

headline.main: Luckless Hull Pay Penalty as West Ham Snatch Win
headline.print_headline: Luckless Hull Pay Penalty as West Ham Snatch Win
